 *   `GameResult<T>`. Make sure you are comfortable with the
 *   pattern before deep-diving into the database or network
 *   adapters.
 * - @ref tutorial_database — Apply the ServiceLocator pattern to
 *   register a `GameDatabase` and run queries with transactions.
 * - @ref tutorial_networking — Same pattern for
 *   `GameNetworkManager`, plus the `Signal<T>` event dispatch.
 * - `advanced/FOUNDATION_ADAPTERS.md` — deep dive on how every
 *   adapter translates kcenon foundation errors.
 * - `include/cgs/foundation/` — authoritative header directory
 *   for every adapter interface.
 */
